text.tspan: Highly organised and disciplined pharmacy leader with excellent communication and conflict resolution skills.
Competent in managing supplies, reviewing service quality, and maintaining patient confidentiality and
satisfaction. Skilled at ordering, storing, and preparing medications for customer use. Accomplished in
increasing customer satisfaction while improving controls, team operations, and loss prevention strategies.
Checked more than 30 patient orders against histories each day, assessed insurance coverage and counted
Provided patient counselling regarding OTC medications.
Managed weekly schedules and requests for leave.
Used pharmacy software Meditab to verify prescription and insurance information.
Compounded and prepared medications according to prescription orders for more than 160 prescriptions every
Solicited medical history information from patients to provide best and most effective medical advice.
